 "I have an idea." a small round gold disc fell from the cealing. He made a 
copy of part of the disc and gave it to scorpinok. The original went back up 
to the cealing. "This is part of the third golden disc. Its message will be 
activated by his dna alone. It will intise his return to this base." He 
turned his back to scorpinok. "Now go."

--part1_8b.1426b47.279a0f86_boundary
